summary: This is an email from 'Wetjets' sent on July 21, 2020, requesting assistance in locating and forwarding photographs taken of an unnamed individual (likely a victim) during the time of Epstein. The sender encloses two pictures from 2008 or 2009 to help identify the person and authorizes providing the pictures to the recipient and another unnamed party.

keyFacts: The email seeks to locate and provide photographs of an individual taken during the 'Epstein' era, suggesting the individual may be a victim or associate.
The sender has been asked by the individual to obtain these pictures 'for years,' indicating a long-standing desire to acquire them.
The sender provides two pictures from 2008 or 2009 to assist in identifying the individual, as they are now 'over a decade older.'
The correspondence authorizes the recipient to provide the enclosed pictures to the individual and another unnamed party.
The document originates from West Palm Beach, FL, a location significant to Epstein's activities.
